{"id":623254,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/【-麻辣总局】耿爽模拟器上线-填啥就强烈谴责/","date":"2019-11-30T06:58:07Z","modified":"2019-11-30T09:04:38Z","title":"【麻辣总局】“耿爽模拟器”上线 填啥就强烈谴责啥","content":"<p>11月29日，继<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e5%9e%8b%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e6%ad%a6%e5%99%a8%ef%bc%9a%e8%b5%b5%e5%bc%b9%e7%a3%81%e9%93%81/\">“赵弹磁铁”</a>之后，有网友开发的另一政治恶搞式的语言随机生成应用—— 耿爽模拟器 -v0.1上线，它可以通过在简单的页面上输入“你想谴责的国家（对象）”以及“对方干了什么事情”而生成“外交部答记者问”式的样板回复。</p>\n<p>访问<a href=\"https://xwgmdjc.github.io/GengShuang/\">地址</a></p>\n<p>简单的主界面：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623255\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复.png 886w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复-300x175.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复-768x449.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>填入“美国”（谴责国家）及“通过香港人权与民主法案”（对方干了什么事情）后生成的效果如下：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-scaled.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623256\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-scaled.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"232\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-scaled.png 2560w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-300x116.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-1024x396.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-768x297.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-1536x595.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-2048x793.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/外交部回复2-1080x418.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>经过网友的反复测试，填入不同国家与谴责理由，会形成数个答问版本（具体几种未知），但生成结果整体让人感到违和感不强，这也说明外交部式的日常答问是有多么僵化与模式化，有网友甚至调侃“外交部发言人可以下岗了”。</p>\n<p>以下为几个网友恶搞版本：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">津巴布韦与安全套 by oranoranskum</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623260\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"797\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD.jpeg 1241w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD-188x300.jpeg 188w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD-643x1024.jpeg 643w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD-768x1223.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD-964x1536.jpeg 964w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmKzQmUwAAWgHD-1080x1721.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">习近平与复辟帝制 by wulebao</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmThwFUcAAIYd0.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623261\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmThwFUcAAIYd0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1055\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmThwFUcAAIYd0.jpeg 568w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmThwFUcAAIYd0-142x300.jpeg 142w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKmThwFUcAAIYd0-485x1024.jpeg 485w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">化州市与反对建火葬场 by xiaobeast8</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-623262\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1283\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW.jpeg 798w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW-117x300.jpeg 117w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW-399x1024.jpeg 399w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW-768x1971.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/EKlzogMXsAAuObW-599x1536.jpeg 599w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>从版本号上看，该应用或将进行后续的升级，一名<a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/9938\">自称作者</a>的品葱网友称这个应用的原理很简单，“把耿爽的发言摘录下来，然后进行简单的随机组合，再替换掉关键字即可。效果居然相当不错，毕竟耿爽翻来覆去就那几句话。”并欢迎网友们参与测试。</p>\n","author":972,"categories":[18271,38912,13789],"tags":[39409,14912,17827,39408,39411,39401,39410]}